    <h2>What separates our Fire Magic service from general grill repair.</h2>

    <ul class="reasons-list">
      <li><strong>Echelon Diamond expertise.</strong> The Magic Window, Diamond Sear grids, master switch LED system, Power Burner: these aren't generic grill components. We know them.</li>
